Lagos State police command recently at the Ojuwoye market in Mushin area of the state arrested one Mr. Benjamin Ojukwu for allegedly adulterating wine and hot drinks. Ojukwu was arrested following intelligence report on the orders of CP Edgal Imohinmi by ACP Akinbayo Olasoji and his men who stormed Ojuwoye Market on 30th day March, 2018 for selling adulterated wine and hot drinks. The suspect, Ojukwu told our correspondent that he actually learnt how to make wines and hot drinks in China. “I was in China to learn how to mix and produce wines and hot drinks and when I got back to Nigeria in 2015, I started my own business in Nnewi, Anambra State. “I had to relocate to Lagos to start afresh when my factory got burnt,”Ojukwu confessed. He also confessed to have been refilling branded bottles with his own products so as that consumers can patronise him till he is able to promote his brand. On how he plans to achieve his brand dream while adulterating other brands, the 55-year-old suspect said he was going to achieve that after making enough profit from adulterating other brands. Meanwhile, CP Edgal Imohinmi has vowed to get to the root of the crime by working with relevant agencies to ensure the needful is done. Recovered from the suspect are Labeled bottled corks of different types of wine and spirits, empty wine bottles and various brands of wine, hot drinks, spirits suspected to be adulterated. 0 comments Do you get a good or bad response from your wife after making love? Discover a great natural solution that changed my story and put an end to weak/premature ejaculation, CLICK HERE.  100% Natural Solution To Premature Ejaculation, Weak Erection, Watery Sperm, Other Sexual Dysfunctions And Last More Than 30 Minutes During Sex.